{"questionId":"19198","questionHtml":"<p>Show that&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>A'&nbsp;B'&nbsp;C'&nbsp;D'</mtext></math>&nbsp;is a parallelogram.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>Grad&nbsp;A'B'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>8</mn><mn>9</mn></mfrac><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;Grad&nbsp;C'D'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>8</mn><mn>9</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>therefore&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>A'B'</mtext></math>&nbsp;is parallel to&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>C'D'</mtext></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>R1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>Grad&nbsp;A'D'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>6</mn><mn>12</mn></mfrac><mo>;</mo><mtext>&nbsp;Grad&nbsp;B'C'</mtext><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mn>6</mn><mn>12</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>therefore&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>A'D'</mtext></math>&nbsp;is parallel to&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>B'C'</mtext></math></p>\n<p>therefore&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mtext>A' B' C' D'</mtext></math>&nbsp;is a parallelogram&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>AG</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong><br>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"19198","referenceCode":"20N.1.AHL.TZ0.F_7b.iv","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Show that A' B' C' D' is a parallelogram.","paper":"1","level":"AHL","questionNumber":"b.iv","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","Topic 3—Geometry and trigonometry","AHL 3.9—Matrix transformations"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}